// RESET mid-execution. Drive a non-trivial pattern (LD HL,nn + INC HL loop)
// so that PC, HL, I, R, IFF have all advanced beyond reset state by the
// time the reset pulse arrives. After reset, PC/I/R must be 0 and the
// core should resume fetching at 0x0000 (visible as an M1 with addr=0x0000).
@0000
21 34 12           // LD HL,0x1234
23                 // INC HL
23                 // INC HL
00 00 00           // NOPs
C3 03 00           // JP 0x0003  (loop on INC HL)
